{"tid":1209781,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"梁競徽：唔怕有影響","createTime":"2019-06-12T12:19:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T06:42:34.000Z","uid":1121,"like":190,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"a2a46c685a92013955c66addb925edf3022fd841","tid":1209781,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T12:19:18.000Z","msg":"梁競徽說：「是，今日張相整靚了，和陳小春那張好真，張相其實是拍《鐵探》在隧道爆車時，是袁偉豪影的。（怕否事情帶來影響？）應該不會，上網咁耐知邊張（相）真定假，唔介意，開玩笑啫。（內地粉絲在不知情下鬧你？）無鬧啦，明白他們緊張，所以已經放了和三哥（苗僑偉）拍《飛虎》時的原相。（怕否下次又「被遊行」？）<span style=\"color: red;\">無得怕唔怕，控制唔到</span>。」"},{"pid":"6856df546afeec2bc63acb933fa3dca7350f4628","tid":1209781,"uid":1121,"like":101,"dislike":1,"score":100,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T12:20:06.000Z","msg":"明白哂，大家心照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ec218d23c9d8ff164394844b87991fd3f99dd26","tid":1209781,"uid":141278,"like":69,"dislike":0,"score":69,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T12:23:17.000Z","msg":"控制唔到打警察？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nking fight 真英雄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6014a844b44c2e10c143af453fe38ebf9daef18b","tid":1209781,"uid":27210,"like":109,"dislike":1,"score":108,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T12:34:19.000Z","msg":"話就話同路人<br />\n但雙面人到咁真係驚驚地<br />\n好難想像衝到最前個個係佢..."},{"pid":"71a701076730c443de4e3bafbfe81579f114ab7e","tid":1209781,"uid":67903,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T12:37:07.000Z","msg":"香港最大群既潛在罪犯 警犬..<br />\n<br />\n勁fight哥面對呢班大罪犯都可以淡定應對,又救走眾多義士...respect"},{"pid":"0c95ba4ebdc3ef01fd738c8d2b2952d808a5caf9","tid":1209781,"uid":152123,"like":5,"dislik